MAHBUBNAGAR : In a high profile battle whose outcome had significant impact for both the parties , Congress candidate Vamshi Chander Reddy won the Kalwakurthy Assembly seat , the results of which were declared on Monday after repolling was held in a booth .
With this , the Congress has secured 21 seats in the 119 Telangana Assembly and will be the principal opposition party .
